on-color: initial;"><span style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">*1</span> Inorder to take advantage of cadmeister&#39;s performance, it is recommended that the graphics engine be<br style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;">configured for GA.<br style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;">How to set up the graphics engine is described in the CADmeister online help.<br style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;">CADmeister Online Help&rarr; Customization&rarr; &quot;Graphics Engine&quot;</p><p style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;margin: 0px 0px 10px;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">*2</span> The Japanese version of CADmeister has been confirmed to work only on the Japanese OS.<br style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;">The English version of CADmeister has been confirmed to work only on the English OS.<br style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;">The Chinese version of CADmeister is confirmed to work only on the Chinese version of the OS.</p><p style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;margin: 0px 0px 10px;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">*3</span> If the display of the operation window is disturbed, please make the following settings.<br style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;">On the Start button, right-click it. Select Search from the list of menus.<br style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;">In the search term, type Windows Design and Performance Tuning, and then select from the list of search results that appear.<br style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;">On the Visual Effects tab, select Prioritize Performance.</p><p style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;margin: 0px 0px 10px;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">*4</span> The DieStacker function is not eligible, but operation confirmation is carried out.</p><p style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;margin: 0px 0px 10px;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">*5</span> It can not longer be installed on operating systems that are not supported from CADmeister 2022.</p><p style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;margin: 0px 0px 10px;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">*6</span> It will not be available for installation on Windows&reg; 2023.8 (1-bit version) from CADmeister 64.</p><p style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;margin: 0px 0px 10px;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">*7&nbsp;</span>CADmeister uses the Windows 10 Universal CRT, so if you are using an OS earlier than Windows 10, you will need to apply the update. Download and apply the update for your OS from the official Microsoft website.<br style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;">URL: <a href="https://support.microsoft.com/ja-jp/topic/windows-%E3%81%A7%E3%81%AE%E6%B1%8E%E7%94%A8%E3%81%AE-c-%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%82%BF%E3%82%A4%E3%83%A0%E3%81%AE%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E3%83%97%E3%83%AD%E3%82%B0%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A0-c0514201-7fe6-95a3-b0a5-287930f3560c" style=" border-box;outline: none medium !important;backgr