 in the Visual effect tab.</p><p style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;margin: 0px 0px 10px;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;font-weight: 700;"><span style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">*4</span></strong>Although DieStacker is not officially supported on the support OS, its operability has been tested.</p><ul style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 10px;list-style-type: none;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;"><li style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;">Intel and Pentium, and Core2 Duo are the trademarks or registered trademark of Intel Corporation or its affiliates in the United&nbsp;States and other countries.</li><li style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;">Microsoft, Microsoft Excel, and Internet Explorer are the registered trademark or trademark of Microsoft Corporation in the United States and in other countries.</li><li style=" border-box;outline: 0px !important;">The formal name of Windows is Microsoft Windows Operating System.</li><li style=" border-box;outline: 0px !impo